:

*Prošla* godina bila je teška. (The past year was hard.)
*Prošlo* leto je bilo veoma vrelo. (Last summer was very hot.)
*Prošle* nedelje smo bili na odmoru. (We were on vacation last week.)
*Prošli* mesec bilo je veoma hladno. (It was very cold last month.)
*Prošlog* vikenda smo se odmarali. (We were relaxing last weekend.)